title: Vols rally to 38-31 win over No. 19 Georgia; Chubbs injured
text:
> Georgia Vols rally to 38-31 win over No. 19 Georgia; Chubbs injured Tennessee head coach Butch Jones, left, shakes hands with Georgia head coach Mark Richt after Tennessee won 38-31 in an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Knoxville, Tenn. (AP Photo/Wade Payne)
